thread.title: Zanskar

author: Zanskar
title: Zanskar
text: I ordered a few audio products online which were coming from stores in different states. The prices were great, communication was fast and I was called by the team to confirm my order and be notified where each of my items were coming from and the approximate shipping time. I received the items as advertised and in very fast time- only a couple days! I loved that I got free shipping and I'll definitely reconnect Store DJ to my audiophile friends.
